OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,FThe victim of two so-called builders
OL,7,Ffrom Kent who conned customers out of
OL,8,Fmore than #1.3million says they
OL,9,Fshould've been stopped sooner.
OL,11,FSamuel O'Hanlon and Jack Sargeant were
OL,12,Fjailed for a combined 15 years and
OL,13,Fnine months for defrauding 12 victims
OL,14,Fby demanding huge sums of cash and
OL,15,Fmaking up bogus excuses to stop
OL,16,Fworking.
OL,18,FKent Trading Standards says it is the
OL,19,Fbiggest case its ever investigated.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
