FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780607468
OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,FHowever, Liz Hennessey, from Ashford,
OL,7,Fsays warning signs were missed by the
OL,8,Fauthorities and the damage went far
OL,9,Fbeyond the stolen money.
OL,11,F"I cannot blame his (my husband's)
OL,12,Fdeath on these people but what I can
OL,13,Fsay is that they absolutely destroyed
OL,14,Fthe last couple of years of his life,"
OL,15,Fshe said.
OL,26,@sD@UpmsD@bpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
