CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780607468
OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,FWith his health deteriorating, Liz and
OL,7,Fher husband, Paul, put their trust,
OL,8,Fand #60,000 of their savings upfront,
OL,9,Fin Samuel O'Hanlon to build a ground
OL,10,Ffloor extension at the home they'd
OL,11,Floved for more than 40 years.
OL,13,FBut it was all a calculated scam
OL,14,Fdesigned to extract as much money as
OL,15,Fpossible, whilst inventing extra jobs
OL,16,Fthat didn't need doing.
OL,18,FLiz said: "We got to the point where
OL,19,Fwe would dread him ringing on the
OL,20,Fdoorbell because you knew there was
OL,21,Fgoing to be another problem.
OL,26,@zD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
