OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1780607468
OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,F"By the end of May, we were forced to
OL,7,Flive in one room with a toaster and a
OL,8,Fkettle. That is not a cowboy builder.
OL,9,FThat is a criminal."
OL,11,FWhile the judge called him the
OL,12,Fringleader, O'Hanlon was not working
OL,13,Falone. He had Jack Sargeant, 28, as
OL,14,Fhis apprentice in the fraud.
OL,26,@qD@TO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
