OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,FTogether they operated through three
OL,7,Fdifferent companies: Bespoke Homes,
OL,8,FAdvanced Contractors South East, and
OL,9,FPrecision Contractors South East,
OL,10,Fconning Liz and eleven other
OL,11,Fhomeowners out of more than one
OL,12,Fmillion pounds.
OL,14,FDuring an an eightweek trial, the
OL,15,Fcourt heard that many of those
OL,16,Ftargeted were in circumstances that
OL,17,Fmade them particularly susceptible to
OL,18,Fpressure and false reassurance.
OL,20,FThat trust was deliberately exploited
OL,21,Fto secure early and repeated payments.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
