OL,3,CCowboy builders: Victim says
OL,4,Cfraudsters ruined husband's final years
OL,6,FSeveral victims were left living for
OL,7,Fprolonged periods in partially
OL,8,Fdismantled or unsafe homes, with
OL,9,Fadditional and substantial costs
OL,10,Frequired to make their properties
OL,11,Fhabitable again.
OL,13,FIndependent expert evidence later
OL,14,Fconfirmed that large amounts of the
OL,15,Fwork carried out was substandard and
OL,16,Fwould require significant remedial
OL,17,Faction.
OL,19,FHow can you stay safe?
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
